---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About Hanif Carroll"
	description="Product Engineer with end‑to‑end ownership across discovery, UX, and delivery."
>
  <div class='container space-y-16 py-12'>
    <section class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.4fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] md:items-start">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-primary/80">About</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50 sm:text-5xl">
          I’m a Product Engineer who likes shipping 0→1.
        </h1>
        <p>
          I work across product discovery, UX, and full‑stack delivery. I’ve shipped scheduling and reporting systems (LeagueApps, Nearsure), internal enterprise tools (Capgemini), and led small teams in freelance roles as a fractional CTO.
        </p>
        <p>
          I’m most useful to small teams that need clear decisions, fast iterations, and pragmatic engineering. I care about user outcomes, developer ergonomics, and keeping systems boring where they should be.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-base">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span> End‑to‑end: research → prototyping → delivery → instrumentation.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span> Tech: React, TypeScript, Next.js, Node.js, Tailwind, Docker.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span> Product: user research, strategy, MVP development, agile.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
        <img
          src="/img/portrait-professional-desktop.webp"
          alt="Hanif Carroll"
          loading="lazy"
          class="max-w-sm rounded-3xl border border-zinc-200 shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800"
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Experience at a glance</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <li><strong>Freelance (2024–now):</strong> Fractional CTO for a social events platform (led 2 juniors); delivered a portfolio site; built a Webflow catalogue; launched landing pages with GA/Hotjar insights.</li>
          <li><strong>Nearsure (2023–2024):</strong> Improved scheduling UX for 3,000+ sports organizers; optimized mobile editing flows.</li>
          <li><strong>LeagueApps (2021–2023):</strong> Reduced scheduling time by 45% with a drag‑and‑drop grid; conflict detection; reporting with AG Grid; component library with Styled Components + Storybook.</li>
          <li><strong>Capgemini (2019–2021):</strong> App for cruise ship and crew management; led schedule reporting; cut test runtime by ~60%; delivered KPI dashboards.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">How I work</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <li>Write decisions. Prefer boring tech where it helps speed and reliability.</li>
          <li>Instrument from day one; measure activation and retention, not just output.</li>
          <li>Keep scope tight; ship to learn; iterate with real user feedback.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="pt-2 flex gap-4">
          <a class="underline" href="mailto:HanifCarroll@gmail.com">Email</a>
          <a class="underline" href="https://linkedin.com/in/hanifcarroll" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
          <a class="underline" href="/Hanif_Carroll_Product_Engineer.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resume</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
